{"tid":2078712,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好驚老豆老母","createTime":"2020-06-25T08:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T08:09:41.000Z","uid":255802,"like":19,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"563cf71368bf5904cc20019089e75c6d0ffbd152","tid":2078712,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:58:54.000Z","msg":"由細到大唔係打就係鬧<br />\n「你大個去砵蘭街做雞都冇人要」<br />\n我好記得佢係我小學咁講<br />\n<br />\n得閒當你係出氣袋<br />\n發你脾氣係天經地義 <br />\n因為佢話 係佢十月懷胎生你出黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n樓豬係出左黎翻工了<br />\n比老細屌都未有唔開心過<br />\n啱啱比老母鬧到喊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪得我一個先會咁驚自己老母<br />\n我都幾撚肯定自己有童年創傷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後有句 我次次睇到都會想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幸福的人用童年治癒一生<br />\n不幸的人用一生治癒童年"},{"pid":"f2ea9d64b26e17b2b3011237459c2b3fdcd00f8d","tid":2078712,"uid":6783,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:59:50.000Z","msg":"永遠支持169"},{"pid":"5d270f6778da6dc0bd580f5a9a640b0245413ce5","tid":2078712,"uid":360656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:02:09.000Z","msg":"推薦你睇 《被討厭的勇氣》，希望對妳有幫助。"},{"pid":"c7a282cdf3cfc5ec326dba70db92ac2300e8b7ff","tid":2078712,"uid":114754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa9be7bbbbd4f5823f505474321b617ea472cc1","tid":2078712,"uid":206337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:05:14.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"d6e22cab6b5b79a217204af06b6c92404d2eaf80","tid":2078712,"uid":8089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef44acc597beaec231b906811a964ff8d26a3fc7","tid":207